reviewText: I thought this DVD came with everything but fabric to learn to put this quilt together, but it's just a DVD, no foundation papers and no direction as to where to get the foundation papers. Of no use without the foundation papers, impossible to follow along without them, making this DVD worthless. Will be returning.
I would love to meet Jacqueline De Jonge and take her class! What an inspiration and her work is just awesome! She is my new quilt hero!
This kit with DVD has everything needed except fabric to construct this quilt.  Easy step by step instructions and templates.
